---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout
  title="Experienced Travel Consultants | 10 Billion Travelers"
  description="Discover how our travel consultants at 10 Billion Travelers can tailor your dream vacations."
>
  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <div class="breadcrumb">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <span>About</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="story-section">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h1>Our Story</h1>
      <p class="story-tagline">
        I was born to travel! I've logged over 1 million miles. Before I'm 100 years old there will be 10 Billion people alive. I'll inspire as many travelers as possible!
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Kevin White Bio -->
  <section class="bio-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bio-grid">
        <div class="bio-photo">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=400&q=80"
            alt="Kevin White — founder of 10 Billion Travelers"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p class="photo-caption">Having fun on the Great Wall</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bio-text">
          <h2>Kevin White</h2>
          <p>
            Born in a poor family in Western North Carolina, I had only traveled outside of NC for a few days until I went to college in South Carolina. I didn't even have a passport until I was 30 years old. Today, I've logged over 1 million miles and have traveled to 26 different countries around the world.
          </p>
          <p>
            I love to travel. I love adventure. I love to travel to popular destinations but love even more to sleep under the stars where very few people have ever gone. I know how to travel. I know what makes airlines, hotels, restaurants, and attractions great! I'm blessed with a ton of practical travel experience and would love to share it with you.
          </p>
          <p>
            Check out our Vlogs, Blogs, Reviews, and Travel Services. We will inspire &amp; facilitate your travel dreams. Let us consult with you to make your hotel, restaurant, or attraction more profitable. Are your bags packed yet?
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <h2>Have a Question?</h2>
      <h3>We'd Love to Hear From You</h3>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn" style="margin-top: 24px;">Email Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .breadcrumb {
    padding: 16px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .breadcrumb span {
    margin: 0 6px;
  }

  .story-section {
    padding: 80px 0 40px;
  }
  .story-section h1 {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .story-tagline {
    font-size: 20px;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .bio-section {
    padding: 40px 0 80px;
  }
  .bio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .bio-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 71px;
    aspect-ratio: 283/300;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .photo-caption {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .bio-text h2 {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .bio-text p {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-cta {
    padding: 60px 0 80px;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }
  .about-cta h2 {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .about-cta h3 {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bio-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .bio-photo {
      max-width: 250px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .bio-text {
      text-align: left;
    }
    .story-tagline {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }
</style>
